  <h1>Delete your account</h1>

  <p>To delete your account in <strong>Your App Name</strong>:</p>

  <ol>
    <li>Open the <strong>Your App Name</strong> app.</li>
    <li>Log in with your account.</li>
    <li>Go to <strong>Settings → Delete my account</strong>.</li>
    <li>Confirm the deletion.</li>
  </ol>

  <p>For security reasons, accounts can only be deleted after logging in from inside the app.</p>
